OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775599870
OL,3,CNorth West reports most e-bike and e-
OL,4,Cscooter fires outside London
OL,6,FThe North West has reported the
OL,7,Fhighest rate of e-bike and e-scooter
OL,8,Ffires outside of London, as numbers
OL,9,Freached a record high last year.
OL,11,FFire brigade figures obtained by the
OL,12,FPress Association show 432 e-bike
OL,13,Fblazes were recorded across the UK in
OL,14,F2025.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,17,F(GMFR) reported a total of 42 e-bike
OL,18,Fand e-scooter fires: the highest
OL,19,Foutside of London.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
