CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775599870
OL,3,CNorth West reports most e-bike and e-
OL,4,Cscooter fires outside London
OL,6,FA total of 70 fires were reported by
OL,7,Fservices in the North West. In
OL,8,Fcomparison in 2021, 88 were reported
OL,9,Fin total across the UK.
OL,11,FE-bike and e-scooter fires are often
OL,12,Fcaused by the failure of batteries,
OL,13,Fconversion kits or chargers.
OL,15,FThese products bought from online
OL,16,Fmarketplaces have been found to be at
OL,17,Fgreater risk of malfunctioning than
OL,18,Fthose sold by established retailers
OL,19,Fbecause they are not subjected to the
OL,20,Fsame level of regulation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775599870
OL,3,CNorth West reports most e-bike and e-
OL,4,Cscooter fires outside London
OL,6,FHead of prevention at GMFR Karl
OL,7,FGibbons said: "E-scooters and e-bikes
OL,8,Faren't inherently dangerous in terms
OL,9,Fof the actual product itself but what
OL,10,Fthey do present in terms of risk is
OL,11,Fthe use of lithium iron batteries.
OL,13,F"Lithium iron batteries when they fail
OL,14,Fcan be dangerous. They can burn
OL,15,Fquickly and intensely and can create
OL,16,Ftoxic smoke."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775599870
OL,3,CNorth West reports most e-bike and e-
OL,4,Cscooter fires outside London
OL,6,FHe said GMFR's guidance for e-bike and
OL,7,Fe-scooter safety includes buying from
OL,8,Fapproved retailers, avoiding DIY -
OL,9,Finstead taking them to appropriate
OL,10,Fprofessionals for modifications, and
OL,11,Fensuring you only use the specific
OL,12,Fchargers that are provided.
OL,14,FGreater Manchester ranked second
OL,15,Fhighest in e-bike fires (29) and third
OL,16,Fin e-scooter fires (13) in the UK.
OL,18,FFires involving lithium batteries used
OL,19,Ffor e-bikes and e-scooters can spread
OL,20,Frapidly and produce a toxic vapour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775599870
OL,3,CNorth West reports most e-bike and e-
OL,4,Cscooter fires outside London
OL,6,FVideo shows the result of
OL,7,F"overcharging" a lithium battery used
OL,8,Fto power e-bikes and e-scooters. This
OL,9,Fcan be prevented by only using the
OL,10,Fprovided equipment to charge an e-
OL,11,Fvehicle, and buying from reputable
OL,12,Fretailers.
OL,14,FGiuseppe Capanna, product safety
OL,15,Fengineer at Electrical Safety First,
OL,16,Fsaid there are five times more e-
OL,17,Fscooter and e-bike fires than 2021,
OL,18,Fand a 38% increase since 2021.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775599870
OL,3,CNorth West reports most e-bike and e-
OL,4,Cscooter fires outside London
OL,6,FHe said: "These fires are not like
OL,7,Fordinary fires, they can be really
OL,8,Fferocious. The fires from lithium iron
OL,9,Fbatteries can reach 700C and they
OL,10,Frelease toxic fumes.
OL,12,F"You cannot put these fires out so
OL,13,Fthat's why it's really important that
OL,14,Fpeople are being safe with these
OL,15,Fbatteries and charging them in a safe
OL,16,Fway."
OL,18,FGiuseppe said he mostly sees issues
OL,19,Fwith "substandard" versions of the e-
OL,20,Fvehicles, and buying them from
OL,21,Freputable retailers can decrease risk.
OL,26,@qD@XOX
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775599870
OL,3,CNorth West reports most e-bike and e-
OL,4,Cscooter fires outside London
OL,6,FHe said: "At the moment, online
OL,7,Fretailers are not responsible for the
OL,8,Fitems sold on their sites and that's
OL,9,Fsomething that has to change.
OL,11,F"People are bringing these dangerous
OL,12,Fproducts into their homes and that's
OL,13,Fwhy we're seeing so many fires in
OL,14,Fthese items."
OL,16,FGiuseppe said in some cases, people
OL,17,Fhave died due to charging their e-
OL,18,Fvehicle in an escape route such as a
OL,19,Fcorridor or near their front door,
OL,20,Fwhich have set on fire due to
OL,21,Fsubstandard batteries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
